"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-why-is-there-barely-any-bbc-coverage-of-paris-2024-olympic-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  When you tune intothe BBC coverage of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, it might surprise you to see that there is barely any of it.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Hardy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Hardy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Hardy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Hardy\"}, {\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999945674626131, \"rank\": 5.3244739632308115e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember during London 2012 when you could watch every minute of every sport somewhere on the national broadcaster?\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999987048795, \"rank\": 1.2929931431715199e-09, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well those days are numbered.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because ahead of the 2018 PyeongChang Winter Olympics in 2015 Warner Brothers Discovery bought the rights to European television's coverage of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2018 PyeongChang Winter Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"PyeongChang Winter Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 528, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"score\": 0.6809685617381356, \"rank\": 0.24331097251868844, \"text\": \"Warner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\"}, {\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"score\": 0.9997345178947492, \"rank\": 0.0002648318437995164, \"text\": \"Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999997899067, \"rank\": 1.3888728251679072e-10, \"text\": \"Discovery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their deal goes through until the 2032 summer Olympic Games in Brisbane, Australia, and it has subsequently had consequences for the BBC coverage.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.999962287683177, \"rank\": 1.763768232741347e-05, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}, {\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9951848044051267, \"rank\": 0.004693409886587365, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 757, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999945674626131, \"rank\": 5.3244739632308115e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The $1.3bn Warner Brothers Discovery deal entitles the broadcaster - through Eurosport and Discovery+ - to show every minute of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"score\": 0.6809685617381356, \"rank\": 0.24331097251868844, \"text\": \"Warner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\"}, {\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"score\": 0.9997345178947492, \"rank\": 0.0002648318437995164, \"text\": \"Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\"}, {\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999997899067, \"rank\": 1.3888728251679072e-10, \"text\": \"Discovery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC still has rights, thanks to the government's crown jewels scheme; which protects certain events for free-to-air coverage, but their allowance is diminished.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999945674626131, \"rank\": 5.3244739632308115e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC will have a network stream, which will flick between BBC 1 and 2, and a secondary stream - likely the Red Button but also iPlayer.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999945674626131, \"rank\": 5.3244739632308115e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The broadcaster will therefore show the key events as they happen, or retrospectively, but not everything will be shown live.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC will have 250 hours of coverage but Discovery+ will have every minute of action.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1523, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999945674626131, \"rank\": 5.3244739632308115e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A subscription can be found online.\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": []}]}"